THIRD-PARTY LICENSES

This project uses the following open-source projects:

1. Tauri (https://tauri.app)
   License: MIT / Apache 2.0
   Used for: Desktop application framework (Rust backend wrapper)

2. Svelte (https://svelte.dev)
   License: MIT
   Used for: Frontend UI framework

3. TypeScript (https://www.typescriptlang.org)
   License: Apache 2.0
   Used for: Type-safe JavaScript

4. Vite (https://vitejs.dev)
   License: MIT
   Used for: Frontend build tooling

5. Monocraft Font (https://github.com/IdreesInc/Monocraft)
   License: SIL OFL 1.1
   Author: Idrees Hassan
   Used for: Minecraft-inspired pixel font (contains no Mojang assets)

6. Tokio (https://tokio.rs)
   License: MIT
   Used for: Async Rust runtime

7. Serde & Serde JSON (https://serde.rs)
   License: MIT / Apache 2.0
   Used for: Serialization/deserialization (YAML, JSON)

8. Reqwest (https://docs.rs/reqwest)
   License: MIT / Apache 2.0
   Used for: HTTP client

Please see https://github.com/voidhamsterofficial/mc-server-manager/blob/main/src-tauri/Cargo.toml
for a complete list of Rust dependencies and their licenses.

